original: Johnson, Gurli Ebba Viktoria, läroverksadjunkt, Falkenberg, f. 1/4/87 i Falkenb. av sjökapt. Nikolaus Oscar J. o. Eugenie Augusta Bergström. — Mog :ex. i Halmstad 06, folkskoll :ex. i Landskr. 07, fil. kand. i Lund 13, fil. mag. 14, provår v. södra latin i Stblm 31. Res. t. Engl. 14, Tyskl. 20 o. 29, Schweiz o. Itiail. 21, Ital., Frankr. o. Tyski. 31, Frankr. o. Engl. 37, Schweiz 38, Engl. 39. Folkskoll. i Halmstad 07-11 o. 14-17, e. o. ämneslär. i Borgholm 17-18, ord. 18, i Falkenberg 19, adj. i modersm., tyska o. eng. v. Falkenbergs samrealsk. sed. 40.
translated: Johnson, Gurli Ebba Viktoria, high school teacher, Falkenberg, b. 1/4/87 in Falkenb. of sea captain Nikolaus Oscar J. and Eugenie Augusta Bergström. - M. ex. (teacher's exam) in Halmstad 06, elementary school ex. in Landskr. 07, Bachelor of Arts in Lund 13, Master of Arts 14, probationary year at South Latin in Stblm 31. Traveled to England 14, Germany 20 and 29, Switzerland and Italy 21, Italy, France and Germany 31, France and England 37, Switzerland 38, England 39. Taught elementary school in Halmstad from 07-11 and 14-17, substitute subject teacher in Borgholm 17-18, co-opted in 18, in Falkenberg 19, adjunct in mother tongue, German and English at Falkenberg's secondary school since 40.
